---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import { url } from '../lib/url';
---

<Base title="Chapter Lore">
  <h1>The Angels Encarmine</h1>
  <p class="lede">
    A Blood Angels successor Chapter, inheritors of the blood of Sanguinius, and of its curse.
  </p>

  <div class="prose">
    <!-- PLACEHOLDER: replace this section with your own chapter lore. -->
    <blockquote>
      "We do not hide what we are. We wear the red so the enemy knows whose blood is owed."
    </blockquote>
    <h2>Origins</h2>
    <p>
      The Angels Encarmine were founded from the gene-stock of the Blood Angels, carrying both the
      martial nobility of Sanguinius and the shadow of the Flaw. This page will hold this army's own
      telling of the Chapter: its history, heraldry, and heroes.
    </p>
    <h2>This army</h2>
    <p>
      The collection is a work in progress: two units photographed so far, the rest assembled or in
      the paint queue. Watch the <a href={url('/gallery/')}>gallery</a> grow.
    </p>
  </div>
</Base>
